        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/Ancestral/scene_bulldog.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 92fde65e-f1ad-40df-a21a-347bd4082200).Image",
        "Description": "Good day 47,\r\rLove affairs are disturbing day to day operations in the carlile mansion 47, the gaurds are distracted and the maids are not doing their jobs.\r\rBoth security and maintenance are at risk!\r\rOur client Mr. C has requested that, if you are able, you are to take out the gaurds while the maids are watching.\r\rThe last thing the maids should see is the dead body of their lover before they die.\r\rGood luck 47.",
